function filterCategory(cat){
  // show/hide articles based on data-category
  var cards = document.querySelectorAll('article.card, aside article');
  cards.forEach(function(el){
    var artCat = el.getAttribute('data-category') || '';

      el.style.display = '';
    } else {
      el.style.display = 'none';

  });
